■ Aurum Token — Whitepaper v1.0
Introduction
The Aurum Token represents the idea of Digital Gold. Our vision is to build a token
that symbolizes trust, transparency, and long-term value. Our mission is to grow
step by step with the community, creating something solid and sustainable.
Achievements ■
So far, we have built a strong foundation:
■ Token created and launched on Binance Smart Chain (BEP20)
■ Contract verified and published on BscScan
■ Official Telegram group launched with security bots
■ Official page on X (Twitter) created and active
■ Website live (first version, under ongoing improvement)
■ Report submitted to BscScan for token logo update
Next Steps ■
What we are working on next:
■ Roadmap updates and expansion
■ Presale announcement
■ Listings on exchanges (first DEX, then CEX)
■ Partnerships with trusted projects and communities
■ Utilities: golden pass for holders, payment use cases, and future innovations
Tokenomics
Total Supply: 1,000,000 AUR

Phase 2 — Expansion

Security & Transparency
• Verified smart contract

Conclusion
The Aurum Token is more than just a coin — it is digital gold. This is the first
version of our whitepaper, and future updates will be released as the project
grows. We are building step by step, with transparency, trust, and the strength of
our community.
If you believe in this vision, walk with us — participate, share, and help build.
Digital gold is our future, and together we will move forward.
